ttp_template:
<group name="group_time_rp_flags">
(*, {{GROUP}}), {{TIME}}, RP {{RP}}, flags: {{FLAGS | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="out_if_out_status_out_time">
    {{OUT_IF}}, {{OUT_STATUS | ORPHRASE}}, {{OUT_TIME | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
<group name="source_group_flags">
({{SOURCE}}, {{GROUP}}), {{{{FLAGS | ORPHRASE}}IME}}, flags: T
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value GROUP (\S+)
Value SOURCE (\S+)
Value TIME (\d+:\d+:\d+\/\d+:\d+:\d+)
Value RP (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value FLAGS (\S+)
Value INC_IF (\S+)
Value RPF_NBR (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value OUT_IF (\S+)
Value OUT_STATUS (\S+)
Value OUT_TIME (\d+:\d+:\d+\/\d+:\d+:\d+)

Start
  ^\(\*,\s+${GROUP}\),\s+${TIME},\s+RP\s+${RP},\s+flags:\s+${FLAGS}\s*$$
  ^\s+Incoming\s+interface:\s+${INC_IF},\s+RPF\s+nbr\s+${RPF_NBR}\s*$$
  ^\s+Outgoing\s+interface\s+list:\s*$$
  ^\s+${OUT_IF},\s+${OUT_STATUS},\s+${OUT_TIME}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\(${SOURCE},\s+${GROUP}\),\s+${TIME},\s+flags:\s+${FLAGS}\s*$$
  ^\s+Incoming\s+interface:\s+${INC_IF},\s+RPF\s+nbr\s+${RPF_NBR}\s*$$
  ^\s+Outgoing\s+interface\s+list:\s*$$
  ^\s+${OUT_IF},\s+${OUT_STATUS},\s+${OUT_TIME}\s*$$ -> Record
